header.name: Royston Weekday July 2018 Timetable
header.description:
Welcome to Royston July 2018 Timetable. As you know, there aren't many timetables on Royston where you can challenge yourself with a weekday 2018 timetable. So I thought I'll create one. This is my first timetable so mistakes will definitely be made somewhere.

Previous passenger trains from the previous day conclude between 00:00 to 02:00. From around 02:00, there won't be many trains till the morning rush hour (05:00). You can use the F3 Options menu to increase and decrease the simulation speed. There is a range of empty EMU stock and passenger services in this timetable. 

- Class 365 (London Kings Cross - Cambridge / Ely / Kings Lynn / Royston)
- Class 700/0 (8 cars) (London Kings Cross - Cambridge North)
- Class 700/1 (12 cars) (Brighton - Cambridge)

- Trains with "C" - Stopping services to/from London Kings Cross / Cambridge / Cambridge North)
- Trains with "R" - Semi-Fast services to/from London Kings Cross / Royston
- Trains with "T" - Fast services to/from London Kings Cross / Ely / Kings Lynn
- Trains with "S" - Thameslink service to/from Brighton / Cambridge via Canal Tunnels

GTR (Govia Thameslink Railway) and Great Northern are the only companies to be running on this line

If there are any mistakes or improvements you would like me to make, pls message the "Royston Weekday July 2018 Timetable" forum post. 

References:
Real Time Trains | Departures from Royston Link
(http://www.realtimetrains.co.uk/search/advanced/RYS/2018/08/03/0000-2359?stp=WVSC&show=all&order=wtt) {Last Accessed: 06/08/2018).

With thanks,
Vortexhaha (Nathan)
